<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TNT23">
<l>uḷḷūruñ cintainō yeṉakkē tante</l>
<l>ṉoḷivaḷaiyum māniṟamuṅ koṇṭā riṅkē</l>
<l>teḷḷūru miḷanteṅkiṉ tēṟal māntic</l>
<l>cēlukaḷun tiruvaraṅkam nammū reṉṉak</l>
<l>kaḷḷūrum paintuḻāy mālai yāṉaik</l>
<l>kaṉaviṭattil yāṉkāṇpaṉ kaṇṭa pōtu</l>
<l>puḷḷūruṅ kaḷvānī pōkē leṉpa</l>
<l>ṉeṉṟālu mitunamakkōr pulavi tāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Giving to me mental anguish that seeped inside,</l>
<l rend="indent">he took my bright bangles and dark coloring;</l>
<l>I see in a place of dream</l>
<l rend="indent">him of the fresh tulasī garland where nectar seeps,</l>
<l>As [he] says, “Our city is Tiruvaraṅkam, here where carp leap,</l>
<l rend="indent">drinking seeping, clarified toddy [made from] young coconut fruit”;</l>
<l>When I see him, I say, “You bird-riding thief, don’t go!”</l>
<l rend="indent">Nevertheless, this is [just] pique to us.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
